==Sprinklers==
Sprinklers water crops automatically every morning at 6am. Sprinklers can be used to automatically water troughs in the [[Slime Hutch]] but they cannot water a [[Animals#Pets|pet's]] water bowl. Sprinklers will also not water plants in [[Garden Pot]]s. They cannot be placed on sand. 
